SSAnne_2F_Corridor_Text_ThisShipIsLuxuryLiner::
    .string "This vessel carries a hidden\n"
    .string "COGNIA signal recorder.\p"
    .string "People call it a party ship,\n"
    .string "but the walls keep listening.$"

SSAnne_2F_Corridor_Text_RivalIntro::
    .string "{RIVAL}: Hey, ROAN!\n"
    .string "You really came here?\p"
    .string "This ship is crawling with\n"
    .string "weird sound data.\p"
    .string "My father said COGNIA used\n"
    .string "ships to move early samples.\p"
    .string "You think that proves anything?\n"
    .string "Then beat me first.$"

SSAnne_2F_Corridor_Text_RivalDefeat::
    .string "Tch!\p"
    .string "Your BRAINROTS are getting\n"
    .string "stronger than they should.$"

SSAnne_2F_Corridor_Text_RivalVictory::
    .string "{RIVAL}: See?\p"
    .string "You are chasing ghost stories\n"
    .string "and fake memories.$"

SSAnne_2F_Corridor_Text_RivalPostBattle::
    .string "{RIVAL}: I heard the captain\n"
    .string "knows the old ship codes.\p"
    .string "Maybe he knows why COGNIA\n"
    .string "kept coming back here.\p"
    .string "Do not get the wrong idea.\n"
    .string "I am not helping you.\p"
    .string "I just hate being left behind.$"
